{
  "info": {
    "name": "Booking PDF API",
    "description": "Endpoints to generate and download a Booking Confirmation PDF.\n\n## Setup\n1. Set `baseUrl` (default: `http://localhost:3000`)\n2. Run **Login** first — the token is auto-saved to `token`\n3. Set `bookingId` to the ID you want to generate a PDF for\n\n## Notes\n- The PDF endpoint streams a binary `application/pdf` response directly (no intermediate file URL)\n- In Postman, click **Send and Download** to save the file locally",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "bookingId",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Login to obtain a JWT token.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (Superadmin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.success && res.data && res.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.data.token);",
                  "    pm.test('Token saved', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(pm.collectionVariables.get('token')).to.not.be.empty;",
                  "    });",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"identifier\": \"superadmin_seed\",\n  \"password\": \"superadmin123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login as superadmin. Token is auto-saved to the `token` variable."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Operator Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.success && res.data && res.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.data.token);",
                  "    pm.test('Token saved', function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(pm.collectionVariables.get('token')).to.not.be.empty;",
                  "    });",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"identifier\": \"operator_seed\",\n  \"password\": \"operator123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login as an operator admin. Token is auto-saved to the `token` variable."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Booking PDF",
      "description": "Generate and download a Booking Confirmation PDF.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Generate Booking Confirmation PDF",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response is a PDF', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.headers.get('Content-Type')).to.include('application/pdf');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Content-Disposition header is present', function () {",
                  "    const disposition = pm.response.headers.get('Content-Disposition');",
                  "    pm.expect(disposition).to.include('attachment');",
                  "    pm.expect(disposition).to.include('.pdf');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "description": "JWT token from Login"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/pdf",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "bookings", "{{bookingId}}", "pdf"]
            },
            "description": "Generates a Booking Confirmation PDF for the given booking ID and streams it as a binary `application/pdf` response.\n\n**In Postman:** click **Send and Download** to save the PDF to your machine.\n\n**Authorization:** Requires `booking:read` permission. Operators can only download PDFs for bookings belonging to their own company.\n\n**Response headers:**\n- `Content-Type: application/pdf`\n- `Content-Disposition: attachment; filename=\"booking-{id}.pdf\"`\n- `Content-Length: <bytes>`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Generate PDF – 404 (Booking Not Found)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 404', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(404);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Error message in response', function () {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(res.success).to.eql(false);",
                  "    pm.expect(res.message).to.include('not found');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/999999/pdf",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "bookings", "999999", "pdf"]
            },
            "description": "Expects a 404 when the booking ID does not exist."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Generate PDF – 401 (No Token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 401', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(401);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/pdf",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "bookings", "{{bookingId}}", "pdf"]
            },
            "description": "Expects a 401 when no Authorization header is provided."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Generate PDF – 403 (Wrong Company)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 403', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(403);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "description": "Token of an operator from a DIFFERENT company than the booking's company_id"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/pdf",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "bookings", "{{bookingId}}", "pdf"]
            },
            "description": "Expects a 403 when an operator tries to download a PDF for a booking that does not belong to their company."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
